data.description: PRICE IMPROVEMENT! What an opportunity?! Have you ever wanted to grow your own organic food? This captivating home comes with a vast garden that has recently produced rhubarb, asparagus, strawberries, blueberries and raspberries! Don't forget the quaint green house in back, while you sip on some wine, from your very own vines? Indulge in an assortment of apples, pears, figs & peaches on this "3-lot sized yard!" Newly painted 2022! Newly renovated kitchen & new flooring throughout, this charmer won't last!  Not to mention the possibilities, there is about 300 unfinished sq ft of space, upstairs!  As for the garage, it has a large built in shop (1010sf) and a separate room, perfect for a hobby room!  ADU dreams? This is it!
